/-
# Isomorphisms of Random Dynamical Systems -- L2

RDSIso: an invertible RDS morphism (conjugacy).

## Properties
- rdsIsoId: identity isomorphism
- rdsIsoSymm: inverse isomorphism
- rdsIsoComp: composition of isomorphisms

## Invariance
Isomorphic RDS have the same dynamical properties:
- Same orbit structure (up to bijection)
- Same Lyapunov exponents (for linear RDS)
- Same invariant measures (via pushforward)

Knowledge: L2 Core Concepts
-/

#eval "=== Morphisms.Iso: RDS isomorphisms ==="
#eval "RDSIso = invertible RDSHom (conjugacy)"
#eval "Isomorphisms: reflexive, symmetric, transitive"
#eval "Conjugate RDS have same dynamics"

